{"settings":"{

  "[css]": {

  },

      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": false,
      "italic": false
    },
    {
      "tag": "*",
      "color": "#98C379",
      "strikethrough": false,
      "underline": false,
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": false,
      "italic": false

  "terminal.integrated.env.windows": {},
